metadata.name: full moon collection 2022
metadata.description:
This is a compilation of collections drawn on the theme of full moon names throughout the year.

January: Wolf Moon  
February: Snow Moon  
March: Worm Moon  
April: Pink Moon  
May: Flower Moon  
June: Strawberry Moon  
July: Buck Moon  
August: Sturgeon Moon  
September: Harvest Moon  
October: Hunters Moon  
November: Beaver Moon  
December: Cold Moon
